snippet.title: Whitney Henriquez in her own trap : Witness Exposes the two sisters
snippet.description:
Whitney Henriquez in her own trap : Witness Exposes the two sisters

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

Johnny Depp’s lawyer Adam Wildman has recently released an email from Jennifer Howell to Amber Heard’s sister Whitney. Now, if you don’t know who Howell is, we’ll you. Howell was Whitney’s employer at the charity The Art of Elysium in 2015 and she is also a major witness of Johnny-Amber situation.
